Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.26,0:00:13.24,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Nii-san gave up everything for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.57,0:00:17.74,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}So I'm going to give up what's most precious to me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.99,0:00:30.76,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Why are you throwing it away?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.01,0:00:34.46,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Do you hate it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.46,0:00:35.33,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.81,0:00:38.50,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}But to survive, I have to throw it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.02,0:00:41.02,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Was that the same for me, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.49,0:00:44.71,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I'm not connected to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.67,0:00:49.77,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}People realize they were connected when they no longer are.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.51,0:00:53.41,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I have to protect the connections I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.03,0:00:55.78,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}So I'm giving up soccer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.47,0:01:05.75,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.22,0:01:09.65,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Some dreams come true because you're disconnected.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.98,0:01:16.42,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Of course he wouldn't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.75,0:01:20.44,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I guess this is the last time I see this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.44,0:01:21.73,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Nii-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.73,0:01:22.81,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Is everything okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.81,0:01:23.84,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.84,0:01:24.95,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.41,0:01:29.19,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}But there's a good chance they've sniffed out what happened four years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.74,0:01:34.78,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}You'd better not still be thinking that it's your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.37,0:01:36.70,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.39,0:01:39.11,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Don't forget, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.11,0:01:43.70,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Just as you need me, I need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.70,0:01:46.08,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Come with me, Toi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.43,0:01:47.53,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Nii-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.97,0:01:51.89,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.37,0:01:54.09,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Give me just a little time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.34,0:01:57.80,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}No, I'm going with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.80,0:01:59.29,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I've made up my mind about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.03,0:02:02.90,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}But there are a couple of people I want to make sure are okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.41,0:02:09.10,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I haven't seen you make that face in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.10,0:02:10.88,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Fine, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.88,0:02:12.11,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I'll be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.53,0:02:14.48,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}But only for one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.25,0:02:17.02,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.54,0:03:50.90,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Damn it, Kazuki! That bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.46,0:03:55.46,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Why do I have to take all the flack?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.93,0:03:57.96,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Who's more important, me or him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.38,0:04:01.97,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.97,0:04:03.67,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Out of balls already?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.67,0:04:06.12,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Damn it, everything sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.12,0:04:09.71,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}When everything sucks, just throw it all away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.71,0:04:12.01,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}You only live once.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.58,0:04:15.69,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}You don't get extra lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.99,0:04:24.13,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Holy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.13,0:04:25.49,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}See?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.37,0:04:30.24,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Is there something on my face?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.24,0:04:31.91,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}No, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.91,0:04:34.75,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Oh, here. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.90,0:04:38.26,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Helping people sure does pay off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.02,0:04:40.81,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Tch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.38,0:04:45.41,1080P思源英文标准位置,Reo,0,0,0,,{\blur4}The leader of a fraud ring that was working out of the Tama region...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.41,0:04:46.89,1080P思源英文标准位置,Reo,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Why do we have to deal with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.89,0:04:49.41,1080P思源英文标准位置,Mabu,0,0,0,,{\blur4}The suspect lives in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.74,0:04:51.27,1080P思源英文标准位置,Reo,0,0,0,,{\blur4}So?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.74,0:04:55.43,1080P思源英文标准位置,Mabu,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Apparently, he's wanted in connection to a fatal shooting four years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.02,0:04:59.23,1080P思源英文标准位置,Mabu,0,0,0,,{\blur4}If we capture him, we can easily make him a kappa zombie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.10,0:05:05.15,1080P思源英文标准位置,Reo,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Look at this half-baked doll, so eager to please those people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.26,0:05:11.35,1080P思源英文标准位置,Mabu,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Do you honestly think this'll change my mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.01,0:05:19.79,1080P思源英文标准位置,Mabu,0,0,0,,{\blur4}This is only half-baked.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.21,0:05:28.33,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}A-All clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.81,0:05:35.06,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Man, I owe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.06,0:05:36.83,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Do you know this place well?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.37,0:05:41.69,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I used to hang out here with Kazu—my friend—ever since I was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.45,0:05:44.82,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Everything changes before you know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.82,0:05:46.45,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}The town, the people...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.45,0:05:49.82,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Did you do something bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.65,0:05:55.06,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Hey, Specs, how old are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.06,0:05:55.70,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.31,0:05:57.59,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I'm fourteen. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.59,0:05:59.69,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}You're pretty small for fourteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.69,0:06:01.14,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}That's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.67,0:06:02.95,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}My bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.96,0:06:07.30,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I happen to have a brother that's about your age.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.30,0:06:08.21,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.21,0:06:10.91,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I don't know if it's because I haven't kept up with him for a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.91,0:06:13.47,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}but he's gotten so grown-up. He's not cute anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.86,0:06:16.39,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I'm leaving town with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.01,0:06:19.73,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I can't let myself get caught right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.57,0:06:23.53,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.18,0:06:26.99,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}If it's all right with you, I'd like to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.99,0:06:27.91,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.99,0:06:30.99,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Grow up already.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.24,0:06:34.41,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}But aren't you pissed off, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.85,0:06:38.50,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}We could have granted your wish by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.75,0:06:41.93,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I'm disappointed in Enta.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.37,0:06:44.93,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}He lied to us and betrayed us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.93,0:06:47.30,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I'm sure he has his reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.66,0:06:49.43,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}What reasons?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.43,0:06:50.63,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.63,0:06:52.33,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}That's not for me to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.14,0:06:54.41,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.41,0:06:56.00,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}So you two are keeping a secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.00,0:06:58.50,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Why are you siding with Enta?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.50,0:07:00.89,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}No, that's not what I'm doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.89,0:07:01.99,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.99,0:07:03.15,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I'm going to find the dishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.25,0:07:04.65,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.86,0:07:10.59,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Shit. I'm not good at handling these situations...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.42,0:07:13.92,1080P思源英文标准位置,Sara,0,0,0,,{\a6\blur4}Now for the next story, dish.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.92,0:07:16.81,1080P思源英文标准位置,Sara,0,0,0,,{\a6\blur4}The police force has made an emergency deployment
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.81,0:07:20.69,1080P思源英文标准位置,Sara,0,0,0,,{\a6\blur4}in response to the possibility that Kuji Chikai, 25,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.69,0:07:26.83,1080P思源英文标准位置,Sara,0,0,0,,{\a6\fs40\blur4}wanted leader of nefarious fraud ring Shikotama, is hiding out in Asakusa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.42,0:07:29.42,1080P思源英文标准位置,Sara,0,0,0,,{\a6\blur4}Freeze! Freeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.70,0:07:31.94,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I'm out of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.97,0:07:41.48,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I haven't been to Hanayashiki in ages.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.82,0:07:48.73,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}He used to follow me around,all like, "Nii-chan, Nii-chan..."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.21,0:07:51.70,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Before I knew it, he's a different person.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.74,0:07:57.05,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}He's trying to choose between me and his buddies right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.18,0:07:59.17,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Buddies?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.75,0:08:01.85,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I mean, I can't blame him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.30,0:08:06.00,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I made him give up something precious to him, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.73,0:08:12.01,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}That's the end of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.94,0:08:14.86,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Forget about the gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.39,0:08:16.14,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.14,0:08:17.07,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.51,0:08:19.14,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I'll catch up with you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.06,0:08:33.22,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}You gave up everything for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.45,0:08:36.66,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}So I'm going to give up what's most precious to me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.31,0:08:41.87,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}He gave up soccer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.67,0:08:49.59,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}He used to say he wanted to become a soccer player when he grew up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.15,0:08:53.05,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}No...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.89,0:08:54.91,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}...way...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.30,0:08:57.75,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}This miçanga...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.71,0:09:03.30,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}He said he gave the miçanga away, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.30,0:09:04.06,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}To who?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.06,0:09:05.72,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Who did he give it to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.72,0:09:07.86,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I wouldn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.86,0:09:14.07,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I'm sure he wanted someone to remember how much soccer meant to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.82,0:09:17.82,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}He's too earnest, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.82,0:09:23.02,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}He'd put himself in danger or get his hands dirty for my sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.02,0:09:25.34,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Even though it's not like I asked him to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.57,0:09:28.83,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.58,0:09:32.84,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I would have done anything for Kazuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.97,0:09:37.79,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}No matter how much you do for someone, if it bears no fruit, it's not worth anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.30,0:09:40.85,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}That depends on how you look at it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.41,0:09:44.93,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Just do whatever will make things easiest for you, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.85,0:09:48.21,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.57,0:10:00.85,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I guess I'm out of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.85,0:10:02.29,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}You are.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.29,0:10:04.75,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Hurry up, take your brother, and leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.25,0:10:09.24,1080P思源英文标准位置,Yasu,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Chikai...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.24,0:10:10.74,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Who the heck is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.74,0:10:11.63,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Oh, shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.63,0:10:15.13,1080P思源英文标准位置,Yasu,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I'm going to avenge my bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.49,0:10:29.25,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}No, I, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.29,0:10:32.82,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.82,0:10:33.65,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Yo, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.65,0:10:35.62,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Are you with Chikai?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.62,0:10:36.65,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}N-No, I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.65,0:10:38.64,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Don't play dumb with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.64,0:10:41.66,1080P思源英文标准位置,Reo,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Over here, policeman!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.66,0:10:43.33,1080P思源英文标准位置,Mabu,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\i1}We're{\i0} the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.33,0:10:45.41,1080P思源英文标准位置,Reo,0,0,0,,{\blur4}This happens all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.41,0:10:47.32,1080P思源英文标准位置,Reo,0,0,0,,{\blur4}What are you doing to that child?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.32,0:10:49.58,1080P思源英文标准位置,Mabu,0,0,0,,{\blur4}You're violating the Firearms and Swords Control Act, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.81,0:10:54.48,1080P思源英文标准位置,Yasu,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I've lived my life until now to kill Chikai.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.92,0:10:54.22,1080P思源英文标准位置,Yasu,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Shit, shit, shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.48,0:10:55.51,1080P思源英文标准位置,Mabu,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Chikai...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.55,0:10:59.23,1080P思源英文标准位置,Mabu,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Are you talking about the wanted fugitive, Kuji Chikai?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.23,0:11:01.55,1080P思源英文标准位置,Yasu,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I'm not letting you popos have him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.55,0:11:05.06,1080P思源英文标准位置,Yasu,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Let him take responsibility for taking out my bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.06,0:11:06.71,1080P思源英文标准位置,Mabu,0,0,0,,{\blur4}This guy's so stuffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.71,0:11:08.10,1080P思源英文标准位置,Reo,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Kuji's gotten away already.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.10,0:11:09.81,1080P思源英文标准位置,Yasu,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Quit babbling!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.83,0:11:18.72,1080P思源英文标准位置,Yasu,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.72,0:11:20.41,1080P思源英文标准位置,Reo,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Stay out of our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.41,0:11:23.82,1080P思源英文标准位置,Mabu,0,0,0,,{\blur4}We're in the middle of the street, but oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.82,0:11:27.08,1080P思源英文标准位置,Yasu,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Do you think you can threaten me with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.08,0:11:29.58,1080P思源英文标准位置,Reo,0,0,0,,{\blur4}We'll open this door for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.46,0:11:33.33,1080P思源英文标准位置,Reo,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Desire or love?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.11,0:11:57.66,1080P思源英文标准位置,Reo,0,0,0,,{\blur4}What do we do with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.66,0:12:00.02,1080P思源英文标准位置,Mabu,0,0,0,,{\blur4}He's valuable kappa zombie material.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.02,0:12:01.49,1080P思源英文标准位置,Cop 1,0,0,0,,{\blur4}What was that gunshot?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.49,0:12:03.49,1080P思源英文标准位置,Cop 2,0,0,0,,{\blur4}There's a man down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.49,0:12:06.33,1080P思源英文标准位置,Reo,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Oh dear, we got caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.33,0:12:07.49,1080P思源英文标准位置,Cop 1,0,0,0,,{\blur4}He's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.84,0:12:09.41,1080P思源英文标准位置,Cop 1,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Did you two shoot him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.41,0:12:11.50,1080P思源英文标准位置,Cop 2,0,0,0,,{\blur4}This isn't going to pass as self-defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.81,0:12:15.42,1080P思源英文标准位置,Cop 1,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Hey, why don't you two say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.42,0:12:17.50,1080P思源英文标准位置,Cop 2,0,0,0,,{\blur4}It was Kuji the fugitive who shot him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.49,0:12:19.69,1080P思源英文标准位置,Cop 1,0,0,0,,{\blur4}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.69,0:12:23.51,1080P思源英文标准位置,Cop 2,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Kuji made enemies from the incident four years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.51,0:12:24.85,1080P思源英文标准位置,Reo,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.85,0:12:26.59,1080P思源英文标准位置,Reo,0,0,0,,{\blur4}It's Kuji's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.59,0:12:28.14,1080P思源英文标准位置,Cop 1,0,0,0,,{\blur4}But there's no proof of that anywhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.89,0:12:34.93,1080P思源英文标准位置,Mabu,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Who shot this man?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.93,0:12:36.41,1080P思源英文标准位置,Cop 1,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Kuji the fugitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.41,0:12:37.52,1080P思源英文标准位置,Cop 1,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Without a doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.14,0:12:47.57,1080P思源英文标准位置,Sara,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I've been watching them for the past few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.57,0:12:52.54,1080P思源英文标准位置,Sara,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I'm certain that these two people have captured Dark Keppi-sama, dish.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.66,0:12:54.49,1080P思源英文标准位置,Keppi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Reo and Mabu...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.04,0:12:57.92,1080P思源英文标准位置,Keppi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I never thought they'd still be alive, kero.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.92,0:13:01.55,1080P思源英文标准位置,Sara,0,0,0,,{\blur4}And this is our secret anti-otter weapon, dish!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.14,0:13:04.55,1080P思源英文标准位置,Keppi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.55,0:13:10.47,1080P思源英文标准位置,Sara,0,0,0,,{\blur4}It freezes the target solid at the flick of a switch, so we can catch them alive, dish.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.47,0:13:11.56,1080P思源英文标准位置,Keppi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.56,0:13:14.79,1080P思源英文标准位置,Keppi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Then let's first determine their current location, kero.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.59,0:13:19.31,1080P思源英文标准位置,Sara,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Can't fight on an empty stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.31,0:13:20.69,1080P思源英文标准位置,Sara,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Pepper...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.05,0:13:33.30,1080P思源英文标准位置,Sara,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Prince!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.09,0:13:41.35,1080P思源英文标准位置,Keppi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Out cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.82,0:13:43.30,1080P思源英文标准位置,Sara,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Oh no, dish!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.87,0:13:45.88,1080P思源英文标准位置,Sara,0,0,0,,{\blur4}The live broadcast is coming up, dish.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.88,0:13:48.59,1080P思源英文标准位置,Sara,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I can't be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.59,0:13:50.46,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}You're so horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.46,0:13:51.58,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I thought I was dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.58,0:13:54.63,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}The bad ones are the ones who survive in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.63,0:13:58.29,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Softies like you should be careful, Specs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.29,0:13:59.60,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}You think {\i1}you{\i0} have the right to say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.60,0:14:04.74,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Well, now that you're still alive, you should go make up with your buddies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.23,0:14:07.01,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}No, I don't really...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.01,0:14:10.44,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.44,0:14:12.02,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Share those with your buddies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.62,0:14:16.53,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Hey, Masa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.53,0:14:18.46,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I'm taking a boat there now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.99,0:14:21.38,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Toi's coming, too, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.30,0:14:26.38,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Jinnai?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.38,0:14:27.74,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}About Yasaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.74,0:14:29.44,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Why didn't you say anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.44,0:14:30.09,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.09,0:14:33.14,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}About the miçanga you gave Kazuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.55,0:14:35.81,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}He remembered?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.63,0:14:38.89,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}No, I don't think he realizes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.89,0:14:40.09,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.95,0:14:42.07,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.07,0:14:43.90,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Why didn't you tell Kazuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.48,0:14:46.75,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}He doesn't remember anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.75,0:14:49.15,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}There's no reason to tell him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.82,0:14:53.06,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}You two go on as the golden duo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.59,0:14:55.16,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Are you happy with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.78,0:14:58.63,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I'm going to live for my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.09,0:15:00.91,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.47,0:15:08.02,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}You're such a bad liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.39,0:15:14.78,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Not here, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.15,0:15:21.55,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}This was where I first met him, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.06,0:15:29.47,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I used to think Toi was scary and bad news.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.26,0:15:48.23,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.59,0:15:51.13,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Toi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.13,0:15:52.94,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I don't need the dishes anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.59,0:15:55.10,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I'm leaving town.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.38,0:15:58.35,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Wh-What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.88,0:16:00.74,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Are you angry about what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.71,0:16:03.77,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.77,0:16:05.05,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.23,0:16:09.11,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Hang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.53,0:16:10.85,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I'll do something about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.85,0:16:12.45,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Please don't leave, Toi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.43,0:16:16.81,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}People realize they were connected when they no longer are.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.81,0:16:17.69,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.69,0:16:19.12,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.09,0:16:22.75,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I have to protect the connections I have left.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.75,0:16:26.85,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Toi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.85,0:16:27.59,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Toi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.75,0:16:29.85,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Toi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.49,0:16:42.47,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Toi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.65,0:16:56.24,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Did I make you give up something precious again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.24,0:16:57.78,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.93,0:17:00.69,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}They aren't like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.66,0:17:13.60,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}There you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.60,0:17:14.30,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Kazuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.35,0:17:20.06,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}We have to hurry. Toi's leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.06,0:17:21.56,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}He's really...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.82,0:17:38.32,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}It's your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.32,0:17:42.05,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}It's your fault that Toi's leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.51,0:17:45.32,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Toi could have stayed with us if we had the dishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.32,0:17:46.58,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I feel bad for Toi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.91,0:17:50.07,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}What the hell...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.90,0:17:58.88,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}You keep saying, "Toi, Toi," but you're the worst for forgetting something so precious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.88,0:18:01.58,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}You should have realized what he was trying to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.58,0:18:03.99,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Why would I listen to anything you have to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.50,0:18:06.35,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}You betrayed us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.63,0:18:10.75,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I'm done...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.27,0:18:13.51,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.86,0:18:23.75,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Yeah, well, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.74,0:18:26.31,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.37,0:18:31.13,1080P思源英文标准位置,Reo,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.63,0:18:35.89,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Cops?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.34,0:18:42.64,1080P思源英文标准位置,Reo,0,0,0,,{\blur4}There they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.64,0:18:44.09,1080P思源英文标准位置,Reo,0,0,0,,{\blur4}The Dishes of Hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.14,0:18:45.77,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.77,0:18:48.22,1080P思源英文标准位置,Reo,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Why do we know about the dishes, you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.27,0:18:54.02,1080P思源英文标准位置,Reo,0,0,0,,{\blur4}You don't need to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.02,0:18:57.45,1080P思源英文标准位置,Reo,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Now, it's time to open the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.03,0:19:01.78,1080P思源英文标准位置,Reo,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Desire or love?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.78,0:19:04.02,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Kazuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.31,0:19:33.47,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Enta!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.47,0:19:36.32,1080P思源英文标准位置,Reo,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Do you want to save your friend's life?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.32,0:19:37.95,1080P思源英文标准位置,Reo,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Well, too bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.95,0:19:41.86,1080P思源英文标准位置,Reo,0,0,0,,{\blur4}The Dishes of Hope are going to grant {\i1}our{\i0} wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.86,0:19:43.07,1080P思源英文标准位置,Mabu,0,0,0,,{\blur4}That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.07,0:19:43.57,1080P思源英文标准位置,Mabu,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.57,0:19:46.59,1080P思源英文标准位置,Reo,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Come on, it was just getting good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.59,0:19:47.90,1080P思源英文标准位置,Mabu,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Call for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.90,0:19:49.58,1080P思源英文标准位置,Mabu,0,0,0,,{\blur4}He might still have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.73,0:19:55.33,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Kazuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.99,0:19:57.96,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Enta! Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.96,0:19:59.59,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Why would you do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.57,0:20:07.63,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.37,0:20:10.39,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I couldn't even say it as a joke...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.35,0:20:13.53,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}That I hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.61,0:20:19.55,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}No...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.19,0:20:21.06,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Enta...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.50,0:20:26.14,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Enta!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.54,0:22:42.53,1080P思源英文标准位置,Cop,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Urgent, urgent.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.53,0:22:44.40,1080P思源英文标准位置,Cop,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Emergency orders from headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.40,0:22:48.77,1080P思源英文标准位置,Cop,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Shots fired in the jurisdiction of Asazara Police Station. Shots fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.77,0:22:51.19,1080P思源英文标准位置,Cop,0,0,0,,{\blur4}All units in area to the site.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.87,0:22:53.05,1080P思源英文标准位置,Cop,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Asazara 3 to headquarters.
Comment: 0,0:00:10.26,0:00:13.24,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}中文对话字幕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.26,0:00:13.24,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}哥哥为我放弃了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.57,0:00:17.74,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所以我也要放弃对我而言最宝贵的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.99,0:00:30.76,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}为什么你要把它扔掉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.01,0:00:34.46,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你讨厌它吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.46,0:00:35.33,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.81,0:00:38.50,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但为了生存下去 我必须得扔掉它
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.02,0:00:41.02,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}对我而言也是如此吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.49,0:00:44.71,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我没和任何人相连
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.67,0:00:49.77,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}只有在失去联系时人们才会察觉到联系的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.51,0:00:53.41,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我必须保护我拥有的联系
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.03,0:00:55.78,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所以我要放弃足球
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.47,0:01:05.75,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}拿着它
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.22,0:01:09.65,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}有时候切断某些联系才能让你梦想成真
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.98,0:01:16.42,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}他肯定早忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.75,0:01:20.44,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我觉得这是我看这里的最后一眼了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.44,0:01:21.73,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.73,0:01:22.81,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}没事儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.81,0:01:23.84,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.84,0:01:24.95,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}谁知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.41,0:01:29.19,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不过他们很可能得知了四年前的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.74,0:01:34.78,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你别老自责 那事儿并不是你的错
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.37,0:01:36.70,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}没有
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.39,0:01:39.11,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}当然也别忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.11,0:01:43.70,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}正如你需要我一样 我也需要你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.70,0:01:46.08,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}悠 跟我来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.43,0:01:47.53,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.97,0:01:51.89,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.37,0:01:54.09,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}给我点儿时间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.34,0:01:57.80,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我还是要跟你走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.80,0:01:59.29,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我已经做好决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.03,0:02:02.90,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我只是想看看几个人 确保他们没事儿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.41,0:02:09.10,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我好久没看到你这样的表情了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.10,0:02:10.88,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}没事儿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.88,0:02:12.11,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我会等着的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.53,0:02:14.48,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但只等一天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.25,0:02:17.02,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.54,0:03:50.90,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}可恶 一稀那个混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.46,0:03:55.46,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}为啥得要我来泄漏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.93,0:03:57.96,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是我还是他重要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.38,0:04:01.97,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.97,0:04:03.67,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}已经没球了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.67,0:04:06.12,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}该死 简直糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.12,0:04:09.71,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}如果事情都糟透了 把他们抛掉就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.71,0:04:12.01,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}人生只有一次
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.58,0:04:15.69,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}可没有多余的生命给你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.99,0:04:24.13,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真的……
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.13,0:04:25.49,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.37,0:04:30.24,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我脸上有什么东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.24,0:04:31.91,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}没啥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.91,0:04:34.75,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}给你这个 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.90,0:04:38.26,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}帮助他人总有回报
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.02,0:04:40.81,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}切
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.38,0:04:45.41,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Reo,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在多摩地区实施欺诈的团体的头目离开了那里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.41,0:04:46.89,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Reo,0,0,0,,{\blur4}为什么非得我们来做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.89,0:04:49.41,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Mabu,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嫌疑人在这片街道里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.74,0:04:51.27,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Reo,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.74,0:04:55.43,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Mabu,0,0,0,,{\blur4}很明显 他因为和四年前的枪击谋杀案有联系而被通缉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.02,0:04:59.23,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Mabu,0,0,0,,{\blur4}如果我们抓住了他 就能轻而易举地将他变成河童僵尸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.10,0:05:05.15,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Reo,0,0,0,,{\blur4}看看这个半生不熟的人偶先生 热切地希望讨好他人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.26,0:05:11.35,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Mabu,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你真认为这能说服我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.01,0:05:19.79,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Mabu,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这玩意儿还没烤透啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.21,0:05:28.33,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这边安全
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.81,0:05:35.06,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这算我欠你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.06,0:05:36.83,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你对这儿很熟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.37,0:05:41.69,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我小时候常和一……我朋友来这儿玩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.45,0:05:44.82,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}世事无常
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.82,0:05:46.45,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}此地此人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.45,0:05:49.82,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你做了什么坏事儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.65,0:05:55.06,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}眼镜仔 你多大了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.06,0:05:55.70,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}呃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.31,0:05:57.59,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我14岁 问这干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.59,0:05:59.69,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你看上去比14岁小啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.69,0:06:01.14,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这跟你没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.67,0:06:02.95,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我的锅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.96,0:06:07.30,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我恰好有个弟弟和你差不多大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.30,0:06:08.21,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.21,0:06:10.91,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我不知道是不是因为我好久没陪他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.91,0:06:13.47,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}他现在变得很成熟了 不再那么可爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.86,0:06:16.39,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我要带他离开这片街道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.01,0:06:19.73,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我现在不能被抓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.57,0:06:23.53,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.18,0:06:26.99,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}如果和你在一块儿不碍事 我愿意帮你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.99,0:06:27.91,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}呃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.99,0:06:30.99,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}大人不生小孩气儿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.24,0:06:34.41,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你难道不生气吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.85,0:06:38.50,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}本来现在就可以给你许愿的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.75,0:06:41.93,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我对燕太很失望
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.37,0:06:44.93,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}他欺骗 背叛了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.93,0:06:47.30,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我相信他做这些是有原因的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.66,0:06:49.43,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}什么原因
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.43,0:06:50.63,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}呃……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.63,0:06:52.33,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这不该我来说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.14,0:06:54.41,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}什么鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.41,0:06:56.00,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所以你俩之间还有什么秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.00,0:06:58.50,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你为啥支持燕太
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.50,0:07:00.89,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我不是我没有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.89,0:07:01.99,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}算了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.99,0:07:03.15,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我这就去找盘子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.25,0:07:04.65,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.86,0:07:10.59,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}可恶 我不擅长处理这种状况……
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.42,0:07:13.92,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Sara,0,0,0,,{\a6\blur4}现在是下一条新闻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.92,0:07:16.81,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Sara,0,0,0,,{\a6\blur4}警察正在开展紧急行动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.81,0:07:20.69,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Sara,0,0,0,,{\a6\blur4}来应对25岁久慈誓的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.69,0:07:26.83,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Sara,0,0,0,,{\a6\fs55\blur4}他是邪恶犯罪团伙Shikotama的头目 正在浅草地区隐匿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.42,0:07:29.42,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Sara,0,0,0,,{\a6\blur4}不许动 不许动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.70,0:07:31.94,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.97,0:07:41.48,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我好多年没去过花屋敷了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.82,0:07:48.73,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}他以前老是围着我转 叫我 {\i1}哥哥 哥哥{\i0} 的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.21,0:07:51.70,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}他和现在可不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.74,0:07:57.05,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}现在他在我和他的朋友之间做出选择
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.18,0:07:59.17,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.75,0:08:01.85,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我的意思是 我当然不能怪他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.30,0:08:06.00,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}毕竟我已经让他放弃了他认为宝贵的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.73,0:08:12.01,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.94,0:08:14.86,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}忘了那把手枪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.39,0:08:16.14,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.14,0:08:17.07,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.51,0:08:19.14,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我待会找你 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.06,0:08:33.22,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}哥哥 你为我付出了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.45,0:08:36.66,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所以我也要放弃对我而言最宝贵的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.31,0:08:41.87,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}他放弃了足球
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.67,0:08:49.59,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}他曾说他长大后想要成为足球运动员
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.15,0:08:53.05,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不……
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.89,0:08:54.91,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}……会吧……
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.30,0:08:57.75,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这个友谊链……
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.71,0:09:03.30,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}他说他会把这个友谊链也送出去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.30,0:09:04.06,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}送给谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.06,0:09:05.72,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}他送给了谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.72,0:09:07.86,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.86,0:09:14.07,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我相信他会把这个友谊链送给能记住他有多么喜欢足球的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.82,0:09:17.82,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}他是认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.82,0:09:23.02,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}他是那种为了我 会赴汤蹈火的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.02,0:09:25.34,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就算我没让他这么去做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.57,0:09:28.83,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我 也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.58,0:09:32.84,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我会为一稀付出一切
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.97,0:09:37.79,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不管你为别人付出了多少 只要没有成果 也就没有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.30,0:09:40.85,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这取决于你怎么看待这个成果的分量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.41,0:09:44.93,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}当然啦 最简单的方式就是做任何你觉得能做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.85,0:09:48.21,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这……
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.57,0:10:00.85,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我觉得没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.85,0:10:02.29,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你说的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.29,0:10:04.75,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}快点儿带着你弟弟离开吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.25,0:10:09.24,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Yasu,0,0,0,,{\blur4}誓……
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.24,0:10:10.74,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}他是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.74,0:10:11.63,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}呃 该死
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.63,0:10:15.13,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Yasu,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我要为我大哥复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.49,0:10:29.25,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不 我 呃……
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.29,0:10:32.82,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嘿 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.82,0:10:33.65,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}哟 小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.65,0:10:35.62,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你和誓是一伙儿的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.62,0:10:36.65,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我不是我没有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.65,0:10:38.64,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}别给我装傻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.64,0:10:41.66,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Reo,0,0,0,,{\blur4}警察在这儿哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.66,0:10:43.33,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Mabu,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\i1}我们{\i0} 是警察
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.33,0:10:45.41,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Reo,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这种事儿太常见了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.41,0:10:47.32,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Reo,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你要对这个小孩儿做啥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.32,0:10:49.58,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Mabu,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你违反了武器控制法哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.81,0:10:54.48,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Yasu,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我要活到杀死誓的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.92,0:10:54.22,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Yasu,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不好不好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.48,0:10:55.51,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Mabu,0,0,0,,{\blur4}誓……
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.55,0:10:59.23,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Mabu,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你在说被通缉的那个逃犯久慈誓吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.23,0:11:01.55,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Yasu,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我不会让你们这些条子抓住他的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.55,0:11:05.06,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Yasu,0,0,0,,{\blur4}让他为杀死我大哥这事儿付出代价
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.06,0:11:06.71,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Mabu,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这人脑子太一根筋了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.71,0:11:08.10,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Reo,0,0,0,,{\blur4}久慈都跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.10,0:11:09.81,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Yasu,0,0,0,,{\blur4}别在那儿唠唠叨叨的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.83,0:11:18.72,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Yasu,0,0,0,,{\blur4}该死
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.72,0:11:20.41,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Reo,0,0,0,,{\blur4}别妨碍我们的事儿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.41,0:11:23.82,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Mabu,0,0,0,,{\blur4}虽然是我们在路中间 但是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.82,0:11:27.08,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Yasu,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你觉得那玩意儿能威胁到我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.08,0:11:29.58,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Reo,0,0,0,,{\blur4}来打开一扇门吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.46,0:11:33.33,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Reo,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是欲望还是爱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.11,0:11:57.66,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Reo,0,0,0,,{\blur4}接下来怎么处理
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.66,0:12:00.02,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Mabu,0,0,0,,{\blur4}他可是宝贵的河童僵尸素材
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.02,0:12:01.49,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Cop 1,0,0,0,,{\blur4}刚刚那声枪响怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.49,0:12:03.49,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Cop 2,0,0,0,,{\blur4}有个人倒地了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.49,0:12:06.33,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Reo,0,0,0,,{\blur4}天哪 我们被发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.33,0:12:07.49,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Cop 1,0,0,0,,{\blur4}他死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.84,0:12:09.41,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Cop 1,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是你俩开的枪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.41,0:12:11.50,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Cop 2,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这可不能被当作正当防卫处理了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.81,0:12:15.42,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Cop 1,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嘿 你俩说点啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.42,0:12:17.50,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Cop 2,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是久慈那个在逃犯杀的他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.49,0:12:19.69,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Cop 1,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你在说啥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.69,0:12:23.51,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Cop 2,0,0,0,,{\blur4}久慈四年前树下了很多敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.51,0:12:24.85,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Reo,0,0,0,,{\blur4}没错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.85,0:12:26.59,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Reo,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这是久慈的锅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.59,0:12:28.14,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Cop 1,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但是这没有证据能证明这件事……
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.89,0:12:34.93,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Mabu,0,0,0,,{\blur4}谁开枪打死他的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.93,0:12:36.41,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Cop 1,0,0,0,,{\blur4}久慈那个逃犯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.41,0:12:37.52,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Cop 1,0,0,0,,{\blur4}毫无疑问
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.14,0:12:47.57,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Sara,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我这几天都在观察他们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.57,0:12:52.54,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Sara,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我确信他俩抓住了黑暗河童王子 dish
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.66,0:12:54.49,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Keppi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}玲央和真武……
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.04,0:12:57.92,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Keppi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不敢相信他们还活着 呱呱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.92,0:13:01.55,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Sara,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这个是我们的秘密反獭武器 dish
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.14,0:13:04.55,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Keppi,0,0,0,,{\a6\blur4}这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.55,0:13:10.47,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Sara,0,0,0,,{\blur4}他能在按下开关后迅速冰冻目标 这样我们就能活捉他们 dish
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.47,0:13:11.56,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Keppi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.56,0:13:14.79,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Keppi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}首先确定一下他们的位置 呱呱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.59,0:13:19.31,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Sara,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不能饿着开打
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.31,0:13:20.69,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Sara,0,0,0,,{\blur4}胡椒……
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.05,0:13:33.30,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Sara,0,0,0,,{\blur4}王子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.09,0:13:41.35,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Keppi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}冻晕了……
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.82,0:13:43.30,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Sara,0,0,0,,{\blur4}哦不 dish
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.87,0:13:45.88,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Sara,0,0,0,,{\blur4}直播马上就要开始了 dish
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.88,0:13:48.59,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Sara,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我不能迟到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.59,0:13:50.46,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你也太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.46,0:13:51.58,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我以为我已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.58,0:13:54.63,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这个世界只有坏人才能生存下去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.63,0:13:58.29,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}像你这样的心肠软的人应该要小心 眼镜仔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.29,0:13:59.60,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你觉得{\i1}你{\i0} 有权这么说我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.60,0:14:04.74,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}既然你现在活着 你应该去和你的朋友和好才是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.23,0:14:07.01,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不 我真的……
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.01,0:14:10.44,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.44,0:14:12.02,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}和朋友们一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.62,0:14:16.53,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嘿 雅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.53,0:14:18.46,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我要坐船走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.99,0:14:21.38,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}悠当然也来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.30,0:14:26.38,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}阵内
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.38,0:14:27.74,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}关于矢逆的事情……
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.74,0:14:29.44,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}为啥你要瞒着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.44,0:14:30.09,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}呃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.09,0:14:33.14,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}友谊链是你送给一稀的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.55,0:14:35.81,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}他想起来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.63,0:14:38.89,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不 他应该没想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.89,0:14:40.09,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.95,0:14:42.07,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.07,0:14:43.90,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}为啥你没跟一稀说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.48,0:14:46.75,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}他记不起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.75,0:14:49.15,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}而且现在也没理由告诉他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.82,0:14:53.06,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你俩可以继续当黄金搭档
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.59,0:14:55.16,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你这样就开心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.78,0:14:58.63,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我要为我哥哥而活了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.09,0:15:00.91,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}再见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.47,0:15:08.02,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你这个大骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.39,0:15:14.78,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这儿也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.15,0:15:21.55,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这不就是我和他初次见面的地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.06,0:15:29.47,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}当时我还以为悠是可怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.26,0:15:48.23,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.59,0:15:51.13,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}悠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.13,0:15:52.94,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我不需要那些盘子了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.59,0:15:55.10,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我要离开这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.38,0:15:58.35,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你——你在说啥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.88,0:16:00.74,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你对这事儿很生气吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.71,0:16:03.77,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.77,0:16:05.05,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}说话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.23,0:16:09.11,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.53,0:16:10.85,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我会想办法解决问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.85,0:16:12.45,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}别走啊 悠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.43,0:16:16.81,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}只有在失去联系时人们才会察觉到联系的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.81,0:16:17.69,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.69,0:16:19.12,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你在说啥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.09,0:16:22.75,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我得保护我剩下的联系
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.75,0:16:26.85,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}悠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.85,0:16:27.59,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}悠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.75,0:16:29.85,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}悠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.49,0:16:42.47,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}悠……
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.65,0:16:56.24,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你又因为我放弃了什么宝贵的东西了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.24,0:16:57.78,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.93,0:17:00.69,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}他们并不宝贵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.66,0:17:13.60,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.60,0:17:14.30,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}一稀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.35,0:17:20.06,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我们得快点儿 悠正准备走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.06,0:17:21.56,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}他真的……
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.82,0:17:38.32,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这是你的错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.32,0:17:42.05,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是你让悠离开的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.51,0:17:45.32,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}如果我们有盘子 悠应该和我们在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.32,0:17:46.58,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}悠真的可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.91,0:17:50.07,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.90,0:17:58.88,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你老是说着 {\i1}悠 悠{\i0} 的 但遗忘了最重要的事情的你才是最差的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.88,0:18:01.58,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你应该理解他要做的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.58,0:18:03.99,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我为啥要听燕太你说的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.50,0:18:06.35,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你背叛了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.63,0:18:10.75,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}燕太……
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.27,0:18:13.51,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我要和你绝交
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.86,0:18:23.75,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}可我……
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.74,0:18:26.31,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我……
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.37,0:18:31.13,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Reo,0,0,0,,{\blur4}找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.63,0:18:35.89,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}警察
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.34,0:18:42.64,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Reo,0,0,0,,{\blur4}他们在这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.64,0:18:44.09,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Reo,0,0,0,,{\blur4}希望之皿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.14,0:18:45.77,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.77,0:18:48.22,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Reo,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你要问 {\i1}我们是怎么知道这些盘子的{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.27,0:18:54.02,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Reo,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你没必要知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.02,0:18:57.45,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Reo,0,0,0,,{\blur4}到开门时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.03,0:19:01.78,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Reo,0,0,0,,{\blur4}欲望还是爱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.78,0:19:04.02,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}一稀
