Comment: 0,0:02:29.06,0:02:33.46,1080P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}OP
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.06,0:02:33.46,1080P思源英文标准位置,OP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Once the background blends together,there's an invisible street corner
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.46,0:02:38.05,1080P思源英文标准位置,OP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}There we are, crying out with fading voices
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.05,0:02:42.72,1080P思源英文标准位置,OP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Go forth with the tearing pain
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.72,0:02:47.35,1080P思源英文标准位置,OP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}As though you'd just crawledaway from the worst night ever
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.35,0:02:51.52,1080P思源英文标准位置,OP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}You're always alone
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.52,0:02:56.16,1080P思源英文标准位置,OP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Your heart is shouting a sound of desire
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.16,0:03:01.78,1080P思源英文标准位置,OP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}If we can ever talk again,if we can ever connect
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.78,0:03:05.52,1080P思源英文标准位置,OP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I'd be overwhelmed
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.62,0:03:08.66,1080P思源英文标准位置,OP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}You grow more and more distant
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.66,0:03:11.37,1080P思源英文标准位置,OP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I chase after you
